===Etymology===
Named by its discoverer [[w:Paul Emile Lecoq de Boisbaudran|Lecoq]], after {{L.}} ''[[Gallia]]'' ‘France’, with a play on ''[[gallus]]'' as a translation of ''Lecoq''.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈgælɪəm/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# A chemical element (''symbol'' Ga) with an [[atomic number]] of 31; a soft bluish metal.

====Synonyms====
